Gunday -LRB- English : Outlaws -RRB- is a 2014 Indian action thriller film written and directed by Ali Abbas Zafar and produced by Aditya Chopra .
The film features Ranveer Singh , Arjun Kapoor , Priyanka Chopra and Irrfan Khan in the principal roles .
The film starts off in the 1970s , with the introduction of 2 young boys : Bikram and Bala , who initially become gun carriers and later coal bandits .
They ultimately grow up to become the most powerful goons of Calcutta .
The film was released on 14 February 2014 .
The film also released in Bengali with a full Bengali soundtrack also composed by Sohail Sen. Though , in some of the Bengali songs , the singers differ from the original .
This was also the first Indian film to have its trailer premiere at the Dubai International Film Festival .